#Text=The use of celebrities for voiceovers
#Text=David Shankbone : You ’re known for speaking about the use of famous actors to do voice-over .
#Text=What is your central problem with their use ?
#Text=Billy West : My problem is that if they were judged by the same standards we were , that we have to try and get work with , they would be pretty piss poor as voice performers .
#Text=What standards are those ?
#Text=The standards are that you have a really special voice that you can go around and do that voice and make a living that people just instantly love it .
#Text=Nobody is just instantly in love with the usual suspects .
#Text=Voices that we see in the cartoon movies now .
#Text=Like Robin Williams ?
#Text=No , he 's different , he understands character .
#Text=I mean he understands characterization and voice changes .
#Text=And so does Mike Myers and so does Eddie Murphy .
#Text=Jerry Seinfeld as well in Bee Movie ?
#Text=No , that ’s not it because he‘s doing a character that looks exactly like him and sounds exactly like him .
#Text=I mean , Will Smith does characters that are drawn to look like him and sound like him .
#Text=I wish I had that luxury .
#Text=Nobody draws a character that looks like me and sounds like me for me to just step in and be the perfect person for the role .
#Text=You know what I mean ?
#Text=What ’s the solution ?
#Text=Not to do characters around stars ?
#Text=The thing is , I do n’t have an issue with the fact that these movies are being made .
#Text=If I could audition for them and I did n’t get them , I still would n’t have an issue with them .

#Text=But this is the thing : they audition us for these movies and then they play it for the A-list people , for these celebrities , so they can strip my talents ’ abilities and kind of toss them over to the celebrity just to make it look better than it would be .
#Text=And I ’m not a teacher .
#Text=Not a paid teacher .
#Text=I do n’t like that stuff .

#Text=They audition us for these movies and then they play it for the A-list people , for these celebrities , so they can strip my talents ’ abilities and kind of toss them over to the celebrity just to make it look better than it would be . — West on laying down cartoon characters in auditions , only to have a celebrity end up doing the voice with the quirks West 's voice introduced .
#Text=They ’ll have you come in , or someone of your caliber come in , and actually shape the voice around the character and then they ’ll present it to the celebrity as the template ?
